<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Data CreatedBy="admin" CreatedOn="634110981626253934" UpdatedBy="admin" UpdatedOn="634143019674379470">
  <Properties />
  <Nodes>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement1" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[The example]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement1"><![CDATA[<p>The example contains the <em>ComboBox</em>, which has <em>DataSource </em>as table 'Customer' of <em>DataBase </em>that contains 'CustomerID', 'ContactName' and other columns. 'CustomerID' property is set such as ValueMember and 'ContactName' property is set such as <em>DisplayMember </em>for the <em>ComboBox</em>.</p><p><br />Change selected item of the <em>ComboBox </em>Text of 'Selected value' and 'Selected Name' TextBoxes will be changed.</p>]]></Paragraph>
    <Header Code="HeaderElement2" Type="Subtitle" ShowInTOC="0"><![CDATA[General Info]]></Header>
    <Paragraph Code="ParagraphElement2"><![CDATA[<p>The Visual WebGui <em>ComboBox </em>contains the following properties for binding data:<br /><em>DataSource </em>&ndash; defines the data source that the connector binds to;<br /><em>ColorMember </em>&ndash; defines the color member of the data sources;<br /><em>DisplayMember </em>- specifies the name of an object property that is contained in the collection specified by <em>DataSource </em>property. The property is displayed as text of the item. The default is an empty string (&quot;&quot;);<br />ValueMember &ndash; defines value of the <em>ComboBox </em>item. Represents the name of an object property that is contained in the collection specified by the <em>DataSource </em>property. The default is an empty string (&quot;&quot;);<br />ImageMember - defines image for the <em>ComboBox </em>item. Represents the name of an object property that is contained in the collection specified by the <em>DataSource </em>property. The default is an empty string (&quot;&quot;);<br />And the following events:<br /><em>DataSourceChanged </em>&ndash; occurs when value of the <em>DataSource </em>property is changed. <br /><em>DisplayMemberChanged </em>&ndash; occurs when value of the <em>DisplayMember </em>property is changed.<br /><em>ValueMemberChanged </em>- occurs when value of the <em>ValueMember </em>property is changed.</p>]]></Paragraph>
  </Nodes>
</Data>
